Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:18.65,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}也知道這不過是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:23.46,EDCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}每當遇到挫折
