Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自小就喜歡繽紛小鳥的畫冊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛往不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環繞不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終顏色凝固在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繽紛小鳥漸漸死去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.66,0:00:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分悲慘的結局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  為何我會這麼嚮往繽紛小鳥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是沒法觸及那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法觸及Gold  Saw
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.68,0:02:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Gold  Saw依然被困在她的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能為力了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來試試
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Rock  Shooter裡的真透
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對沙耶的呼喚有反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  萬一你去了那邊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屬於我們的她就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.09,0:03:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我不去的話  真透就無法得救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透是個不可思議的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨  嫉妒  煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很少會有這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如說  她很痛恨煩惱本身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛恨煩惱？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她否定煩惱的自己  想幫助煩惱的他人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種心情  形成了Black  Rock  Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了幫某人解脫煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時也要抹殺掉某人的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Rock  Shooter一定會把屬於我們的她打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就再也無法呼喚真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼好像前提就是要她消失一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這個意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.42,0:04:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和真透兩人都不會消失  我不會讓她們消失
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.36,0:04:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來承蒙你照顧了  沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒來  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音  是優嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  我不會原諒你傷害她的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.61,0:06:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要繼續互相傷害了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望你再戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要輸  你要盡力想著脫離那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:07:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫離這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  想著脫離Black  Rock  Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大喊出來  這個人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black  Rock  Shooter不是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說姐姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  老是傻乎乎的  經常丟三落四
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵吵鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  雖說是自己的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實話說  是個挺好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  看起來像個好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像沒什麼存在感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得  雖然性格開朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不願意打開心扉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會說漂亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親經常出差  我還擔心她會感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她從來沒有怨言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有點覺得她太成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負面的話一句也不說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太乖了  反而讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是給她的壓力太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  真透  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒有傷心事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有煩惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家其實都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能夠相互理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.68,0:09:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直  都希望能這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭猶豫不決地煩惱著的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭會有憎恨他人之心的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是不想傷害自己的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想自己被人嫌棄的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.73,0:09:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自小就喜歡繽紛小鳥的畫冊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後染成一片漆黑的繽紛小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.47,0:10:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其實在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過  嚮往著骯髒的繽紛小鳥罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的繽紛小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  Black  Rock  Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想受傷  這有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有錯  真透
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透你想錯了  你沒有逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.50,0:11:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好地面對現實解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避的不是真透
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避的不是真透  是誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭說我壞話的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老這麼嘰嘰喳喳吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  很痛啊  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優  這孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊  吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放著我不管吧  會救我的吧  吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我們這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要向我提意見？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.47,0:12:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是另一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有義務要保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧  Strength！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打招呼也未免太遲了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣真透
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得好像至今我的Strength都受你關照一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Strength…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是神足優
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在Strength和你一樣在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像有什麼非常痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就是想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎想不起來比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有人看到黑衣同學了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.22,0:15:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學今天不是休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才接到她家裡的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是從昨天起就沒回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？離家出走？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是被綁架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家安靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜  安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  黃泉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了初中生  成為了同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅如此…但是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這麼心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察啊  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真的不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個地方好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我也會去找的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  那麼重要的時候卻請假
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  那麼再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strength…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優居然是Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.89,0:17:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優的心裡有著深刻的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這個世界中戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實世界中少女們的痛苦和煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孕育了這個世界和我們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本來沒有感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是遵從少女們的感情  依靠本能戰鬥著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的世界裡  Black  Rock  Shooter出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到她非常強大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只會戰鬥的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝負和我毫無相關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是在死亡前的一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.49,0:18:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了優的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬間我擁有了感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:19:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優的痛苦是別的少女無法比擬的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.65,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有巨大的質量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是這樣的質量影響了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首次產生感情的我  不禁這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優的感情基本都是由痛苦和憎惡構成的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我抱著全部感情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Black  Rock  Shooter殺了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優還會剩下什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.51,0:19:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有死太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你死了  我可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.53,0:19:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我消失的話  你的煩惱也會消…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的世界很痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡是些殘酷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:19:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡是些痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.29,0:20:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你現在抱著我的煩惱死去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又會產生新的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那時你不在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此相比  這邊的世界簡單多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.82,0:20:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛是最顯而易見的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  和我換一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互換？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.17,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  互換
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會留在這個世界裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在現實裡由你來承受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  Strength
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你背負這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是求你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替我保護那個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為  只有那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能成為她的保護傘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想思考
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  明明好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這名字起得好聰明！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起…去看五彩繽紛的萬物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回去就和小鳥遊同學一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和黃泉一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.93,0:22:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.29,0:22:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會想要忘記真透呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.34,0:22:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真透！
